title: Street Fighter Alpha 3 Max - Working on fw1.5 [Yoshaw]
description:
Just copy paste the extracted 3 folders to the root of your memorystick. Start RunUMD and press X(no need to press O). You&#039;re good to go.

Note: These files are already patched. No need of changing. Just copy paste and play. By &#039;Yoshaw&#039;.

Thanks to those who made the fix available at ps2nfo and uber thanks to those who made the fix(Mr. W).

Note: Doesn&#039;t save but who cares for that. The game plays fine and It&#039;s just a 2D fighter!
